docs.text: Welcome to my Notes I am using this site to record my study notes. I am not sure if everything is correct, so if there are any errors please let me know and I will correct them. Thank you. In this project i use mkdocs to building my study notes , and VS Code and Typora to edit the document. For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files.
